            div
                h2 Challenges and Reflection
                p The four-week time constraint presented a challenge to our team. We had 3 weeks to establish the art direction and complete the graphic assets, and 1 week to finish the microsite prototype. We approached this by having clear role delegations, while still being flexible in assisting other team members when necessary and giving timely feedback. We adopted a more agile approach, simultaneously carrying out planning, design, and prototyping phases.
                p Through this project I familiarized myself with Figma, applied various design principles, and learned to improve my work through image treatment, font pairings, and layout design. It also taught me about design thinking methodologies and collaborating with a team in a short time. 


